The new securely system of the password for log into the application is installed.
For trusted protection of Your data, the password has to fulfill to the following requirements:
∙ The password shouldn't contain 3 identical digits.
∙ The password shouldn't contain 3 consecutive digits.
∙ The password shouldn't consist of 4 consecutive digits of mobile number.
∙ The password shouldn't consist of 4 consecutive digits of a series of the identity card.
∙ The password shouldn't contain Your day/month/year of birth.
∙ The password shouldn't contain the last 4 digits of Your card.
Verification of these requirements will be generated when you change or create a password.

New features:
1) My bonuses.
Now make payments and transfers became not only fast, but also profitable.
Making daily payments and transfers via Unibank Mobile - You will get bonuses.
A new section has been created – My Bonuses.
You can exchange your bonuses for different types of services or gifts.
Pay any type of service and payment and get a bonus!
2) FAQ
Any questions? No time to call us? This section is for you. Here you will find answers to the main questions. We have created the section "FAQ" for find quick answers. Settings-FAQ. This section will save your time and efforts. FAQ - useful for all users of Unibank Mobile.
Your time is really essential for us.
3)Transfers into republic
Now, it is possible to make transfers from Unibank cards to cards of other banks. All you need is to enter to the “Transfers” page and choosing one of transfer kinds is enough.
